        },
        "subject": "LU-3806 obdclass: add LCT_SERVER_SESSION for server session",
        "message": "LU-3806 obdclass: add LCT_SERVER_SESSION for server session\n\nAdd LCT_SERVER_SESSION for server session, and separate the\nserver session flag from LCT_SESSION, so to avoid allocating\nsession info for client stack for each server request, if\nclient and server are on the same node.\n\nThis also prevents server crash when lustre module\nis unloaded while IOs are in progress (LU-1165).\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Gregoire Pichon <gregoire.pichon@bull.net>\nChange-Id: I68965374ce53d735186780d2d3f1bf083a0e8658\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_4"
    }
